## Fireproof

---


[Item Condition Type](https://origins.readthedocs.io/en/latest/types/item_condition_types/fireproof)

Checks if the item stack is fireproof.

Type ID: `origins:fireproof`

---

### Examples

```json
"item_condition": {
    "type": "origins:fireproof"
}
```
